<h4>Summary of Employment Restrictions for State Hiring and Occupational Licensing</h4>
<p>In accordance with the Task Force on Inventorying Employment Restrictions Act, a summary of criminal history-based restrictions on state employment and occupational licensing has been compiled for all state agencies included in the Act. The information is based on agency reports submitted to the Task Force and supplemental research of Illinois statutes and administrative codes.</p>
